  "capabilities": [],
  "purpose": "Allowlist/denylist gate controlling which concept actions the SyncAutomationProvider may invoke at runtime. Each scope holds pattern rules (glob-style action references) grouped by category. Mode determines whether matched patterns are permitted or denied."
